snippet.description:
HEALTHY NATURAL HAIR-INTERVIEW | NATURALISTA AMBER LUSHIOUS CURLS SHARES PROVEN PROCESS & REGIMEN

View Full Video: Simple Steps To Obtain And Maintain Healthy Natural Hair | Naturalista Regimen-Amber_Lushious Curls-Proven Process: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0A7ZGWnl0ac&t=183s

Sisterhood Share Club Contributor and Naturalista, Amber J. Acton shares her regimen for obtaining and maintaining her beautiful healthy natural hair, and 'Lushious' curls. She shares some of her favorite products and her homemade ingredients that really get to the 'Roots' of healthy hair.

1-Wash
2-Condition (Critical Step)
